# Zhama Homepage

This is the Vue 3 + TypeScript + Vite project for Zhama's homepage. The website includes:

- Main landing page
- App download page
- Terms of service and privacy policy pages (both in English and another language)

## Key Files
- [src/main.ts](mdc:src/main.ts) - Entry point of the application
- [src/App.vue](mdc:src/App.vue) - Root Vue component
- [src/router.ts](mdc:src/router.ts) - Vue Router configuration
- [vite.config.ts](mdc:vite.config.ts) - Vite build configuration
- [index.html](mdc:index.html) - HTML entry point
- [package.json](mdc:package.json) - Dependencies and scripts

## Project Structure
- `/src/pages` - Page components for different routes
- `/src/components` - Reusable Vue components
- `/public` - Static assets served as-is
- `/dist` - Built files (generated during build)
